[Cite as 1/29/2004 Case Announcements, 2004-Ohio-345.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

January 29, 2004

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2003-0969. Lumbermans Mut. Cas. Co. v. Xayphonh.

Summit App. No. 21217, 2003-Ohio-1482. This cause is pending before the court on certification of a conflict from the Court of Appeals for Summit County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
